{"tid":2513710,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【香港學校唔會教】文化大革命紅衛兵舉報，將母親推上刑場槍斃。文革離我們愈來愈近？","createTime":"2021-05-02T17:28:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-02T20:40:57.000Z","uid":54517,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"21b5e72eb7a57e849e6cbede23c4128aa55ee862","tid":2513710,"uid":54517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T17:28:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AWx6ygVEoOY&amp;ab_channel=NgSam\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DAWx6ygVEoOY%26ab_channel%3DNgSam&d=LCDPOb8M8FyYKm9nuxOGtZgFNMRZLCTiZeA0y1vO9n4%3D&h=f0b2e887\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AWx6ygVEoOY&amp;ab_channel=NgSam</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f6fc697fa28f14e4fafd889b9e7a345da885297","tid":2513710,"uid":54517,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T17:35:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/mobile/press_review/2013/03/130328_press_son\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fmobile%2Fpress_review%2F2013%2F03%2F130328_press_son&d=LCDPOb8M8FyYKm9nuxOGtZgFNMRZLCTiZeA0y1vO9n4%3D&h=d5785709\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fmobile%2Fpress_review%2F2013%2F03%2F130328_press_son&h=8d1359ee\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/mobile/press_review/2013/03/130328_press_son</a><br />\n<br />\n在方忠謀撕毀和焚燒毛澤東像後，對毛主席滿懷忠心的兒子張紅兵和父親一起向當局告發了她，張紅兵最後一次看見母親，是她在被處死前跪著接受公審。<br />\n<br />\n《衛報》引述一名中國歷史學家的話說，文革中大多數批判父母的子女是因為受到政治壓力，他們被告知要和「反革命」的父母劃清界線，但也有許多子女試圖保護父母不受肉體傷害。而張紅兵的故事卻與眾不同。<br />\n<br />\n毛澤東死後，四人幫被打倒，中國的政治氣候改變了，文革的受害者們能夠為自己正名，方忠謀的弟弟於是向當局要求為姐姐平反，得到張紅兵和他父親的支持。<br />\n<br />\n年近60的張紅兵說，他後來感覺內疚和懺悔，覺得自己作為一個兒子，「連畜牲都不如」。"},{"pid":"d232aae7a1ce57e074a05082f5818d9f74617814","tid":2513710,"uid":36383,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T1